'From Squeak3.1alpha of 28 February 2001 [latest update: #4214] on 30 July 2001 at 9:28:52 am'!"Change Set:		WorldNoCopy-tkDate:			30 July 2001Author:			Ted KaehlerWe used to raise an error when veryDeepCopy tried to copy the World.  Now just (^self) instead, because the world can be a referent in a script.  (If Capitalized Reverences is on, then this is not an issue.)"!!PasteUpMorph methodsFor: 'world state' stamp: 'tk 7/30/2001 09:26'!veryDeepCopyWith: deepCopier	"See storeDataOn:"	^ self isWorldMorph		ifTrue: [self]	"never copy the World"		ifFalse: [super veryDeepCopyWith: deepCopier]! !